name: Cyber Lover
description: Don't have time for a relationship? Sad and lonely? Introducing Cyber ​​Lover! from MindBook. You can try all stages of a relationship - go on dates, start a family, and then get divorced. Voila! You already have experience in a relationship. Don't worry, your data will be safe and MindBook will not share it with third parties. MindBook- we will fulfill your wishes and invent new ones for you! Cyber ​​Lover! is a $579.99 subscription. All overhead costs are borne by the user. Cyber ​​Lover! product can be modified according to your wishes (gender, sexual orientation, worldview). The product cannot be exchanged or returned.
